#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:132
msgid ""
"The `/lead` command can only be used if the *CRM* app has been installed."
msgstr ""
"Der `/Lead`-Befehl kann nur verwendet werden, wenn die *CRM*-App installiert"
